<p><strong>采访人:</strong> Dr. David Rudolph</p>
<p><strong>受访者:</strong> SCP-2996</p>
<p><strong>[开始记录]</strong></p>
<p><strong>Dr. Rudolph:</strong> 下午好，SCP-2996，欢迎来到S-</p>
