<p><strong>附录2996.2：</strong>精神评估采访07/01/2012</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;显示采访</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
